label lexi_date_amusement_park_male:
    scene bg amusement
    show lexi b normal
    with fade
    lexi.say "Come on, [hero.name]…"
    lexi.say "What are you waiting for?"
    lexi.say "A written fucking invitation?!?"
    show lexi b lollipop
    "Normally it would be me sprinting ahead to the entrance of the Amusement Park."
    "All the while trying to drag my date along behind me, despite their attempts to resist."
    "But this is the first time that I've found myself in the reverse of that scenario."
    mike.say "Hey!"
    mike.say "Wait up, Lexi..."
    mike.say "I'm coming as fast as I can!"
    "Putting on a final burst of speed, I manage to catch up to Lexi just as she reaches the gates."
